sentence: please show me all one way first class flights from indianapolis to memphis
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v6.fare_id||'"', '"'||v6.round_trip_required||'"',
 '"'||v7.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v7.class_type||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, flight_fare v5, fare v6, fare_basis v7 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'INDIANAPOLIS'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MEMPHIS'))) AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) 
AND ((v5.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) 
AND ((v6.round_trip_required = 'NO') AND (((v6.fare_basis_code = ANY v7.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v7.class_type = 'FIRST')) 
AND ( 1 =  1)))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' INDIANAPOLIS ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MEMPHIS ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE .
